# Commit message template (lightweight)
#
# Format:
#   type(scope): short summary
#
# Examples:
#   feat(filters): add new NSFW regex for tags
#   fix(validate): handle empty alt-text rules safely
#   docs(readme): clarify usage and examples
#   chore: bump deps and tidy config
#
# Body (optional):
#   - What changed and why (1–3 bullets)
#   - Any user-facing impact or migration notes
#
# Footer (optional):
#   - Closes #123, Related-to #456
#
# Allowed types:
#   feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore
#
# Keep subject ≤ 72 chars; use imperative mood ("add", "update").
